<h2>Seeing in Spanish. From Don Quixote to Daddy Yankee (Sammelband)</h2>
<h3>22 Essays on Hispanic Visual Cultures</h3>
<hr>
<abbr class='unapi-id' title='839'></abbr>
<div class='row-fluid'>
<div class='span8'>
